This paper involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques to identify the author of a text. Therefore, it is most likely to belong to the sub-category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper also incorporates information retrieval techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to the sub-category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR). The use of machine learning techniques further suggests that it could belong to the sub-category of Machine Learning (cs.LG) or Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, since the paper deals with authorship identification, it could also belong to the sub-category of Cryptography and Security (cs.CR).
